casebody.data:
Melissa Kay COOK, et al., petitioners,
v.
Cynthia Ann HARDING, et al. No. 17-1487. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 1, 2018.

Motion of Concerned United Birthparents, Inc., et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Motion of American Association of Pro-Life Obstetricians & Gynecologists, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Motion of 10 Feminist Academics and Advocates for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
